Package: hg2mm
Title: Convert between human and mouse gene orthologs
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dan", "Skelly", , "dan.skelly@jax.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2329-2216"))
Description: This package converts between human and mouse orthologs. The user can choose a variety of methods from returning only one-to-one orthologs, to returning all ortholog relationships, to everything in-between.
